  m_Name: AvatarReference
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  _iraAvatar:
    _nameFinnish: Raivo
    _nameEnglish: Wrath
    _eyeColor: {r: 0.69803923, g: 0.13333334, b: 0.13333334, a: 1}
    _skinColor: {r: 0.8705883, g: 0.54901963, b: 0.4156863, a: 1}
    _frame: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8986eb9b3eef1114f92d2653be2f6cab, type: 3}
    _cornerIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bad414b4c1bae7e4f96d492e83b42bb2, type: 3}
    _character: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 49a83944ee9de1246b10639fa038087d, type: 3}
    _descFinnish: "pystyv\xE4t piilottamaan tunteet kovan ulkokuorensa taakse, mutta
      vaikka vahva olemus suojaakin Egoa kolhuilta, niin kaikella on rajansa."
    _descEnglish: They can hide their emotions behind a tough exterior, but even
      through their strong presence protects the Ego from bruises, everything has
      its limits.
  _avaritiaAvatar:
    _nameFinnish: Ahneus
    _nameEnglish: Greed
    _eyeColor: {r: 0.8, g: 0.8, b: 0, a: 1}
    _skinColor: {r: 0.9098039, g: 0.7607843, b: 0.61960787, a: 1}
    _frame: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f70ad98f7f01db41bafe5dd07c3fd35, type: 3}
    _cornerIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 6e84e4c3a2d400f438be437826ed5abd, type: 3}
    _character: {fileID: 21300000, guid: cd33d7546312a7747acf3596094ed4d7, type: 3}
    _descFinnish: "suojelevat Egoa kohtelemalla tunteita kuin saippuaa - ne lipsautetaan
      pois ja k\xE4\xE4nnet\xE4\xE4n muualle, jotta Ego v\xE4lttyy kohtaamasta niit\xE4,
      samalla j\xE4tt\xE4en muut arvailemaan odottamatonta siirtoa."
    _descEnglish: "They protect the Ego by treating emotions like soap \u2013 they
      slip them away and turn them elsewhere so that the Ego avoids encountering
      them, while leaving others guessing at an unexpected move. "
  _invidiaAvatar:
    _nameFinnish: Kateus
    _nameEnglish: Envy
    _eyeColor: {r: 0.13333334, g: 0.54509807, b: 0.13333334, a: 1}
    _skinColor: {r: 0.54509807, g: 0.5647059, b: 0.5686275, a: 1}
    _frame: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a85f88f04776d5140bd521112cdb8a26, type: 3}
    _cornerIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: afc086fe899f85f4ca33ba72d38a607b, type: 3}
    _character: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 2ee31512d109cfe4e8576046cbbaa0a1, type: 3}
    _descFinnish: "omistavat el\xE4m\xE4ns\xE4 Egon asettamien s\xE4\xE4nt\xF6jen
      noudattamiselle ja ovat valmiita puolustamaan viimeiseen hengenvetoon asti.
      Vankkumattoman lojaaleja, vaikkakin kykenem\xE4tt\xF6mi\xE4 kehittym\xE4\xE4n
      eteenp\xE4in."
    _descEnglish: They dedicate their lives to following the rules set by the Ego
      and are ready to defend them to their last breath. Unwaveringly loyal, yet
      unable to grow or move forward.
  _luxuriaAvatar:
    _nameFinnish: Himo
    _nameEnglish: Lust
    _eyeColor: {r: 0.78039217, g: 0.08235294, b: 0.52156866, a: 1}
    _skinColor: {r: 0.85490197, g: 0.70980394, b: 0.6392157, a: 1}
    _frame: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 801725e4cd15d294182d91861519540c, type: 3}
    _cornerIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: e1f2a882b3e18df4e8d21ca0afe8f5c3, type: 3}
    _character: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 590ee8632f341a34bb09d4e293205e56, type: 3}
    _descFinnish: "ly\xF6v\xE4t Egon vastustajat k\xE4\xE4nt\xE4m\xE4ll\xE4 tunnehy\xF6kk\xE4ykset
      takaisin heit\xE4 vastaan. Pilkan osuessa omaan nilkkaan he ovat kuitenkin
      alttiita luovuttamaan, sill\xE4 he eiv\xE4t kykyne k\xE4sittelem\xE4\xE4n omia
      sotkujaan tai ottamaan vastuuta."
    _descEnglish: "They strike the Ego\u2019s opponents by turning emotions back
      on them. However, when it backfires on them, they become prone to giving up,
      as they cannot handle their own messes or take responsibility. "
  _gulaAvatar:
    _nameFinnish: "Ylensy\xF6nti"
    _nameEnglish: Gluttony
    _eyeColor: {r: 1, g: 0.84313726, b: 0, a: 1}
    _skinColor: {r: 0.91764706, g: 0.7607843, b: 0.63529414, a: 1}
    _frame: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 2c697fa8ec4259f4fbac2ca0121a27b2, type: 3}
    _cornerIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 07133b819c13bae4c8c6cdc3b3205e95, type: 3}
    _character: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 48d783b2cbb52bd468856d539c326df0, type: 3}
    _descFinnish: "kielt\xE4ytyv\xE4t t\xE4ysin tunteiden olemassaolosta ja uhraavat
      itsens\xE4 Egon puolesta, vaikka maksavatkin siit\xE4 kovan hinnan turvautuessaan
      ep\xE4terveellisiin keinoihin."
    _descEnglish: They deny the existence of emotions and sacrifice themselves for
      the Ego, even though they pay a heavy price by resorting to unhealthy means.
  _acediaAvatar:
    _nameFinnish: Laiskuus
    _nameEnglish: Sloth
    _eyeColor: {r: 0.4392157, g: 0.5019608, b: 0.5647059, a: 1}
    _skinColor: {r: 0.7254902, g: 0.7254902, b: 0.7254902, a: 1}
    _frame: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c85d5545634946d4998288d053151ab6, type: 3}
    _cornerIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 4465914b30e24cd4d8b1c38034b54eaf, type: 3}
    _character: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d90e49211f9bcf940862f95c96d7df61, type: 3}
    _descFinnish: "ovat vahvimmillaan oman kuplansa sis\xE4ll\xE4, jonka he ovat
      kehitt\xE4neet Egon suojelemiseksi. Erist\xE4ytymisell\xE4 on kuitenkin hintansa,
      sill\xE4 ilman tukiverkkoaan heist\xE4 tulee eritt\xE4in haavoittuvaisia."
    _descEnglish: They are at their strongest within their own bubble, which they
      have developed to protect the Ego. However, isolation comes at a cost, as without
      their support network they become highly vulnerable.
  _superbiaAvatar:
    _nameFinnish: Ylpeys
    _nameEnglish: Pride
    _eyeColor: {r: 0.5019608, g: 0, b: 0.5019608, a: 1}
    _skinColor: {r: 0.9529412, g: 0.8, b: 0.64705884, a: 1}
    _frame: {fileID: 21300000, guid: fc12ad5b40d27a3408323ac1cbd3e4b4, type: 3}
    _cornerIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7dda66d5aa65dad45b85939de1d20c70, type: 3}
    _character: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bba53856f67f0c24c92f766feeb0f68c, type: 3}
    _descFinnish: "laskelmoivat ja ennakoivat jokaisen liikkeen, jotta tunteet eiv\xE4t
      p\xE4\xE4se yll\xE4tt\xE4m\xE4\xE4n. Heid\xE4n analyysins\xE4 pit\xE4\xE4 Egon
      suojassa, mutta loputon yliajattelu saattaakin vied\xE4 maun el\xE4m\xE4st\xE4."
    _descEnglish: They calculate and anticipate every move so that emotions cannot
      take them by surprise. Their analysis keeps the Ego protected, but endless
      overthinking may drain the joy out of life.
